of 37 passing for zero touchdowns and three interceptions.<ref name=\"Divisional\">[http://www.databasefootball.com/boxscores/gamedata.htm?dy=4&mth=1&yr=1987&tm=NYG&lg=NFL Box Score 49ers Vs Giants 1/4/1987] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060526062832/http://www.databasefootball.com/boxscores/gamedata.htm?dy=4&mth=1&yr=1987&tm=NYG&lg=NFL |date=May 26, 2006 }}, databasefootball.com, accessed May 20, 2007.</ref>\n\n{{Americanfootballbox\n |titlestyle= {{NFLPrimaryColor|New York Giants}}; {{NFLSecondaryColor|New York Giants}};text-align:center;\n |state=autocollapse\n |title=1986 NFC Divisional Playoff: San Francisco 49ers at New York Giants\n |date=January 4, 1987\n |time=12:30 p.m. [[Eastern Time Zone|EST]]\n |road=49ers (10\u20136\u20131)\n |R1=3|R2=0|R3=0|R4=0|RT=3\n |home='''Giants (15\u20132)'''\n |H1=7|H2=21|H3=21|H4=0|HT=49\n |stadium=[[Giants Stadium]]\n |attendance=76,034\n |weather={{convert|31|F|C}}, relative humidity 67%, wind {{convert|15|mph|abbr=on}}, wind chill {{convert|20|F|C}}\n |referee=[[Jerry Markbreit]]\n |TV=[[NFL on CBS|CBS]]\n |TVAnnouncers=[[Pat Summerall]] (play-by-play), [[John Madden (American football)|John Madden]] (color commentator), [[Irv Cross]]\n |reference=[https://www.pro-football-reference.com/boxscores/198701040nyg.htm Box Score]\n |scoring=\n}}\n{{AmFootballScoreSummaryStart|VisitorName=49ers|HomeName=Giants|state=collapsed}}\n{{AmFootballScoreSummaryEntry\n| Quarter=1\n| Time=7:29\n| Team=Giants\n| DrivePlays=\n| DriveLength=\n| DriveTime=\n| Type=RecTD\n| Receiver=[[Mark Bavaro|Bavaro]]\n| QB=[[Phil Simms|Simms]]\n| yards=24\n| kickresult=good\n| Kicker=[[Raul Allegre|Allegre]]\n| Visitor=0\n| Home=7\n}}\n{{AmFootballScoreSummaryEntry\n| Quarter=1\n| Time=1:20\n| Team=49ers\n| DrivePlays=\n| DriveLength=\n| DriveTime=\n| Type=FG\n| yards=26\n| Kicker=[[Ray Wersching|Wersching]]\n| Visitor=3\n| Home=7\n}}\n{{AmFootballScoreSummaryEntry\n| Quarter=2\n| Time=7:39\n| Team=Giants\n| DrivePlays=\n| DriveLength=\n| 